*liquid-2.5.0 (13 Mar 2013)

  13 Mar 2013; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +liquid-2.5.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  13 Mar 2013; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -liquid-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

*liquid-2.4.1 (22 Aug 2012)

  22 Aug 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +liquid-2.4.1.ebuild:
  Version bump and add ruby19 for bug 432254.

  16 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> -liquid-2.2.2.ebuild,
  liquid-2.3.0.ebuild:
  Remove old; bump to EAPI=4; use the testrb-2 helper for testing.

